'''Aɣecter''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: '''Vulpes zerda''') d yiwet ger [[talmest|telmas]] n [[abareɣ|iburaɣ]] yettidiren deg [[aneẓruf Ameqran|uneẓruf ameqran]] n [[Tafriqt n Ugafa|Tefrikt n ugafa]] yakk d kra n yideggan deg [[Tazunegzirt Taserɣint|tzunegzirt Taserɣint]].<br/>
Llan kra n [[asnudran|imusnawen n tesnudert]] iy [[Tasartut n tesnudert|ssesmilen]] aɣecter d [[Tawsit (tudersent)|tawsit]] tasimant (Fennecus), maca imusnawen niden ssesmilen-t deg tewsit n [[tiburaɣ|tburaɣ]] (''Vulpes''), dɣa d asesmel-a aneggaru i d amaddud.

== Aglam ==
Iɣecter d [[aɣersiw]] meẓẓiyen yakk deg [[tawacult (tasnudert)|twacult-is]] ([[taydiyyin]], anda [[azuk|azuk-is]] ur yugar ara 1,5 kg, ma d tiddi-ines alamma d tuyat 20 cm. Ma d teɣzi n tfekka-ines 40 cm. [[Asallaf|Asallaf-is]] 25 cm, [[Ameẓẓuɣ|Imeẓẓuɣen]] n iɣecter d wid igan meqqer-it yakk ɣef wid-ak n taydiyyin niden, acku teɣzi-nsen ttawaṭ ɣer 15 cm. Ayen id t-ittallen  deg twakksa n [[aẓɣal|weẓɣal]] yernan ɣef tfekka-ines mi ara ad zrin [[idammen]] seg [[Amig n idammen|yimigen n idammen]] yellan s waṭas deg umeẓẓuɣ n iɣecter. Akken daɣen i d-tettallen deg tmesliwt n [[tagemra|tgemrawin-is]].<br/>
Ini n weglim n iɣecter d awraɣ am [[ijdi|yijdi]] ayen id s-yettaken [[asengel]] deg twennaṭ anda yettidir.

== Ansayen d tudert ==
Iɣecter yettidir deg [[angu|wengu]] ɣezzifen yettwaɣzen ar 10 n imitren yal angu ttidiren dges aṭas n iɣectren ɣef anect-a iga d netta i d [[talmest]] tamyiwent deg taydiyyin yettidiren deg tegrawin, Yal tagrawt dges [[awtem]] d kra n [[Tawtemt|twetmin]] maca deg kra n wakuden yettidir yakk d twetmin ugar n yiwen n uwtem i wakken ad aggẓen (ad ḥedden ɣef) tagrawt, Maca iwtmen ayi isennawen ttwazraben seg tegrawt mi ara ad [[aberber|bberbren]].

== Učči ==
Iɣecter d [[aɣersiw]] [[aramma]], Armud-is yettidil deg [[iṭ]] anda [[agmar|iy gemmer]] [[timseɣẓaẓ]] am [[aɣeṛda|iɣeṛdayen]] d [[idwi|idwa]] yakk d [[aburɣas|iburɣas]] d [[tazermemmuyt|tzermemmuyin]] d [[aylal|iylalen]] akk d tmellalin-nsen, Maca tuget deg-sen tetten [[imɣi|imɣan]] am [[igumma]] d iẓuran.

== Amyaraw ==
[[Tawtemt]] tessuddus (tessewjad) iman-is i [[amercel|wmercel]] s ukessel n uzagur-is ɣef [[awtem|uwtem]] id tferren s iman-is, awtem agejdan yezmer ad immircal yakk d waṭas n twetmin ma d awtem asennay yettmircal anagar d yiwet n tewtemt neɣ tikwal ur yettmircal ara yakk, Tasemhuyt n umercel yettili-d gar n [[Yennayer]] d [[Meɣres]], Seld n [[Tadist]] yettaṭafen azal n 52 n wussan tettarew-d tewtemt 5 n ikzan (ameẓyan n uɣecter), Dɣa tawtemt tettarew yiwet n tikkelt deg useggas maca llant tikwal dgi id tettarew snat n tikkal deg useggas.

== Agrad n iɣecter ==
Iɣecter iga d [[talmest]] tamyiwent n [[abareɣ|iburaɣ]] i yezmer ufgan ad tyig d [[aɣersiw amegrud]] maca ur [[agrad|tessegraden]] ara s tarrayt tummidt am [[amcic|yimcac]] d [[Aydi|iṭan]] 

